API
Application Programming Interface
API helps to connect/communicate/exchage data between two applications.
API connection happens via HTTP/HTTPs protocol
HTTP - HyperText Transfer Protocol
HTTPs - HyperText Transfer Protocol Secured
Secured - encrypted.
Hello world -> SGVsbG8gd29ybGQK
HTTP operations:
	CRUD:
		- Create => POST
		- Read  => GET
		- Update => PUT
		- Delete => DELETE